<item>
            <title>[HIVE-1594] Typo of hive.merge.size.smallfiles.avgsize prevents change of value</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-1594</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The setting is described as &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;hive.merge.size.smallfiles.avgsize&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;, however common/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/conf/HiveConf.java reads it as &quot;hive.merge.smallfiles.avgsize&quot; (note the missing &apos;.size.&apos;) so the user&apos;s setting has no effect and the value is stuck at the default of 16MB.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12472492">HIVE-1594</key>
