                            <comment id="12902487" author="goosmurf" created="Wed, 25 Aug 2010 16:00:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just doing a quick grep audit of other settings, I think the following is also mismatched:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the format: hive-default.xml =&amp;gt; HiveConf.java&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;hive.default.partition.name =&amp;gt; hive.exec.default.partition.name&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;I believe HiveConf.java has the correct value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12902512" author="namit" created="Wed, 25 Aug 2010 16:47:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, HiveConf has the correct values always.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you submit a patch for this ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
